column5: A Guys Fairy Tale   Once upon a time, a Prince asked a beautiful Princess... ???Will you marry me????  The Princess said ???NO!???  And the Prince lived happily ever after and rode motorcycles and went fishing and hunting and played golf and dated women half his age and drank beer and scotch and had tons of money in the bank and left the toilet seat up and farted whenever he wanted. The End !!!
...lived happily ever after... haha  Good one.
Okay, now even I think that's funny
My wife wont let me play golf....
